# hooks / lib / utils / types

- **hooks/** — React hooks (`use-cart`, hydration helpers).
- **lib/** — shared server infra (auth, payment, prismadb, logger). See `actions-vs-lib.mdc`.
- **utils/** — generic helpers only (`safe-action.ts`, `datetime-utils`, `is-admin`). No `utils/{domain}/` — domain code in `lib/{domain}/`.
- **types/** — shared TS types and enums.

`lib/` and `utils/` must not import `actions/`.
